Class DocumentHeader

gov.va.chir.model.DocumentHeader
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, org.apache.uima.cas.AnnotationBaseFS, org.apache.uima.cas.FeatureStructure, org.apache.uima.cas.text.AnnotationFS
public class DocumentHeader
extends org.apache.uima.jcas.tcas.Annotation
This header contains meta-data about the doucment, and could be extended to cover the kinds of meta-data that the HL7 CDA document header contains about a clincial record, such as who was the author, provider, patient, when the service happened, when it was reviewed, and the like. Updated by JCasGen Wed Aug 17 13:31:49 EDT 2022 XML source: C:/Users/divitag2/work/softwareRepos/bodyFunction/project/60_03_type-descriptors/target/jcasgen/typesystem.xml
